text: dangnan thami cung mimi hmuban sak hæng hnung sraththa doythi kar sraththa khxng phwk khea ca xanwy prayochn kæ phwk khea nxkcak klum chn khxng yu nu s meux phwk khea sraththa rea di pldpeluxng kar lngthosʹ xan xapys cak phwk khea nı kar mi chiwit nı lok ni læa rea di yud wela raya hnung kæ phwk khea
